Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.77,0:00:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Present Day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.44,0:00:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Present Time
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,/
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.42,0:02:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也想伤害自己吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.51,0:02:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渴望拥有一段心如刀割的回忆吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.61,0:02:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就千万别移开视线…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,/
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.61,0:02:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟有没有谁都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.50,0:02:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们这些用户而言 连线世界里有没有神根本无关紧要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.94,0:02:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.42,0:02:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我把那家伙解决掉再说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.37,0:02:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是杀害其他玩家 你觉得这样很好玩么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.58,0:03:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你说也是白搭 没人能体会其中的乐趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.15,0:03:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然招牌上写的是橘综研
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像橘综研这种大型企业 不太可能做出非法行为
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.17,0:03:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我确实听到过这方面的传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.83,0:03:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传闻？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.36,0:03:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我们为什么能像这样在连线世界中交换情报吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 你在考我？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说的不就是IP么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40\fad(100,100)}IP：Internet Protocol，为计算机网络相互连接进行通信而设计的协议。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.86,0:03:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常我们不会对协议这种东西多加在意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如今第六代协议下的数据吞吐量已经见顶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.61,0:04:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七代…协议
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.14,0:04:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 第七代协议
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.24,0:04:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前各大企业正着手建设相应的基础设施
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦掌控了协议 实际就掌控了连线世界的经济
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.62,0:04:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此各方在这点上始终互加阻扰、纠缠不放
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.12,0:04:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而收拾这一局面的正是——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘综研
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,/
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs40}接连出现异常！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs40}环境内分泌干扰物是罪魁祸首？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs40}“E发动机”发售
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs40}车内3岁儿童 因脱水而亡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.59,0:06:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前不久有人这么问我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“你真的是岩仓玲音吗？”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.03,0:06:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“你的父母是你的亲生父母吗？”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.66,0:06:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.07,0:06:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可笑…对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种问题很可笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.27,0:06:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,/
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.26,0:07:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.12,0:07:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.30,0:07:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我并不相信…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.75,0:07:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什、什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.55,0:07:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音 那不是你干的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.22,0:07:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.97,0:07:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会在装傻吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.44,0:07:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽华 现在还不能断定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.83,0:07:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么玲音你说 真的不是你干的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:08:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你们在说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音 你在连线世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没事了 那一定不是玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧那边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.97,0:08:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs55}…别再使用票据结算了 否则会很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.53,0:09:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs55}…难以置信吧 这么漂亮的人居然有那种兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.43,0:09:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs55}第六代协议有致命的漏洞\N会对连线世界构成极大的安全隐患
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs55}那孩子的房间里每晚都会出现一个身影\N穿着红绿条纹的毛衣 看上去像个小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.92,0:09:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs55}就是那个当红偶像 听说她高中时乘男友的车出过事\N把人碾过之后逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs55}千真万确 我当面问过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.70,0:09:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs55}那幢楼闹鬼可是出了名的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.76,0:09:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs55}深夜把头转向屏幕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs55}会收到公司寄来的邮件 那时公司里应该早就没人了才对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.69,0:10:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs55}Knights其实并不存在 那不过是美国学生开的玩笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.63,0:10:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.66,0:10:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样很好玩吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得有趣吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.48,0:10:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.49,0:10:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在找我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.12,0:10:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说中的神登场了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.44,0:10:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神的定义是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界的造物主？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.38,0:10:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌管世界的全能的统治者？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.50,0:10:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就高估我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果所谓的神 是这个世界普遍存在的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.72,0:10:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 没错 你可以这么称呼我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在对世界的走向稍加干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.43,0:10:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.83,0:10:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该也发觉了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.60,0:10:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前 这个连线世界中就一直存在着另一个你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.37,0:11:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不过只是她投射出的全息影像
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.96,0:11:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是一具肉体
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事 谁会信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.93,0:11:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.81,0:11:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 现实世界的你与现在的你 两者的人格截然不同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己也这么觉得吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.26,0:11:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我还是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.04,0:11:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（玲音是偷窥狂）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.38,0:12:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（偷窥狂）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,/
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.65,0:13:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.65,0:13:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs55}那些传言我没放在心上 别在意\Nfrom 爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪儿？你在哪儿呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝你在哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.78,0:13:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.29,0:13:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝 你在哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,/
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.62,0:13:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底做了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.10,0:13:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在连线世界里做了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.22,0:13:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个我到底做了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.28,0:13:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs55}那些传言我没放在心上 别在意\Nfrom 爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\fs55}正在搜索…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.01,0:14:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和老师做这种事真的可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.08,0:14:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.31,0:14:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明知道 为什么还这么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.80,0:14:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.03,0:15:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道瑞城爱丽丝喜欢谁吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道她做那种下流的事情时心里想的是谁吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.25,0:15:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你散布的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传言是真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.03,0:15:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直在暗中偷窥我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我背地里做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最不想让别人看到的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.11,0:15:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音 告诉我这不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:15:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.04,0:16:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.60,0:16:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会像你一样做那种事！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:16:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.86,0:16:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再这样了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要模仿我所厌恶的那个自己？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.04,0:17:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.78,0:17:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在自杀吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会有体温？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.99,0:17:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要让我感觉到你的体温
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…我不就是玲音你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.56,0:17:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.61,0:17:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.12,0:18:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.50,0:18:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些都是你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.27,0:18:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说过 你一直存在于连线世界之中吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普遍存在于连线世界之中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.63,0:18:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.96,0:18:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论在哪儿 无论在谁身边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.37,0:18:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都时刻存在着你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.65,0:18:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你观察着他人的隐私
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是把这些告诉别人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.61,0:18:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为连线世界的信息就是应该共享 不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.36,0:18:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的这些 全是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.84,0:18:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝她们看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.59,0:18:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们说看到了连线世界中的我 而当时我并不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我还能分辨自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.52,0:18:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的自我就与我同在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.23,0:19:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想拿这种低劣的复制品来混淆视听？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.97,0:19:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.93,0:19:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我真如你所说的那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说什么？玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.33,0:19:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家被玲音偷窥过的这段记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.09,0:19:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相应的信息应该都能消除
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的没错 试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.36,0:19:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你与生俱来的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.67,0:19:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在删除…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.70,0:19:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.41,0:20:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.63,0:20:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音 叫你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.26,0:20:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都忘了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.10,0:20:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.02,0:20:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来真的忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.84,0:20:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.78,0:20:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.47,0:20:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.68,0:20:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.35,0:20:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我想去Cyberia
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.21,0:20:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 真难得
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.46,0:20:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 那么老样子 去我家换衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.42,0:20:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.71,0:20:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次要穿什么去呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.62,0:20:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是真正的我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.10,0:21:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.48,0:21:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 玲音是玲音 我是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.23,0:21:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello NAVI
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.63,0:21:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.00,0:21:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是我 对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.28,0:22:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除我之外的我 根本就不存在 对吧？

